Package: deltapif
Title: Estimate Potential Impact and Population Attributable Fractions with Aggregated Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Rodrigo", "Zepeda-Tello", , "rzepeda17@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Uses the delta method to estimate the Potential Impact Fraction (PIF) 
  and the Population Attributable Fraction (PAF) from aggregated data. It creates 
  point-estimates, confidence intervals, and estimates of the variance. 
